# long-straddle

An easy command line utility to see the break even points for a long straddle.

*Disclaimer*: This tool in no way constitues any form of investment advice.

## Install

`$ go get github.com/joshi4/long-straddle`

## Usage

`$ long-straddle share_price strike_price call_fees put_fees`

